Description.Text: Our hotel features a bilingual staff, complimentary wireless, high-speed Internet access, a well-equipped Business Center and a refreshing outdoor swimming pool with a swim-up bar. For added convenience, we even offer complimentary shuttle service to and from local beaches. 0710 IRT

Located in downtown Cancun, the Radisson Hacienda Hotel Cancun, Mexico combines the architectural charm of colonial Mexico with modern comfort. Our downtown Cancun hotel is just a few minutes from beautiful white sand beaches and area attractions, including Aquaworld.
This 4 stars hotel offers spacious, well-equipped rooms with high-speed, wireless Internet access, cable television, coffee makers and hair dryers.
This beautiful property has architecture reminiscent of a Mexican Hacienda from the 19th century

El Granero Restaurant is open for breakfast 7am-11:30am, lunch 11:30am-5pm and dinner 5pm-11pm. El Patio snack bar located at the pool is open 11am-5pm. Room Service is available from 7:00am until 1am.
The hotel has a small lobby surrounded by tobacco shops.
